ir Henry de Graham - Baron of Dalkeith è nato il circa 1163 nel Dalkeith, Midlothian, Scotland, il suo padre, Peter de Graham - Lord of Dalkeith, aveva 21 anni e il suo madre, Geva of Scotland, aveva 43 anni. Lui sposato Anabel De Faunes circa 1185, nel Angus, Scozia, Regno Unito. Morì nel 1233, nel Corstorphine, Midlothian, Scotland, all'età di 71 anni."},"ja":{"about 1163–1233":"約1163年–1233年","1142–Male":"1142年–死亡","1144–1180":"1144年–1180年","1163–1233":"1163年–1233年","1185–1206":"1185年–1206年","1185–1203":"1185年–1203年","1206–1283":"1206年–1283年","1143–1175":"1143年–1175年","1122–Female":"1122年–死亡","1143":"1143年","1175":"1175年","1142":"1142年","Abt 1159":"約1159年","1185":"1185年","1163":"1163年","1283":"1283年","1180":"1180年","1206":"1206年","1203":"1203年","1233":"1233年","1122":"1122年","1144":"1144年","about 1163":"約1163年","Corstorphine, Midlothian, Scotland":"スコットランドミドロスアンコルストルフィン","Scotland, United Kingdom":"イギリススコットランド","Dalkeith Palace, Midlothian, Scotland":"スコットランドミドロスアンダルケイス","Dalkeith, Midlothian, Scotland":"イギリススコットランドミドロスアンダルケイス","lifeSummary":"Sir Henry de Graham - Baron of Dalkeithが約1163年にスコットランドミドロスアンダルケイスで生まれた時，父Peter de Graham - Lord of Dalkeithは21歳，母Geva of Scotlandは43歳であった。約1185年にイギリススコットランドアンガスでAnabel De Faunesと結婚した。彼は1233年にスコットランドミドロスアンコルストルフィンで71歳で死去した。"},"ko":{"about 1163–1233":"대략 1163년–1233년","1142–Male":"1142년–사망","1144–1180":"1144년–1180년","1163–1233":"1163년–1233년","1185–1206":"1185년–1206년","1185–1203":"1185년–1203년","1206–1283":"1206년–1283년","1143–1175":"1143년–1175년","1122–Female":"1122년–사망","1143":"1143년","1175":"1175년","1142":"1142년","Abt 1159":"대략 1159년","1185":"1185년","1163":"1163년","1283":"1283년","1180":"1180년","1206":"1206년","1203":"1203년","1233":"1233년","1122":"1122년","1144":"1144년","about 1163":"대략 1163년","Corstorphine, Midlothian, Scotland":"스컷랜드 미들로스이언 코르스토르필인","Scotland, United Kingdom":"영국 스코틀랜드","Dalkeith Palace, Midlothian, Scotland":"스컷랜드 미들로스이언 다케이스","Dalkeith, Midlothian, Scotland":"영국 스코틀랜드 미들로스이언 다케이스","lifeSummary":"Sir Henry de Graham - Baron of Dalkeith(이)가 대략 1163년 스컷랜드 미들로스이언 다케이스에서 태어났을 때, 그의 아버지 Peter de Graham - Lord of Dalkeith(은)는 21세였고, 그의 어머니 Geva of Scotland(은)는 43세였다. 그는 대략 1185년 영국 스코틀랜드 앤구스에서 Anabel De Faunes(와)과 결혼했다. 그는 1233년 스컷랜드 미들로스이언 코르스토르필인에서 71세의 나이로 사망했다."},"lv":{"about 1163–1233":"ap 1163. gadu–1233. gads","1142–Male":"1142–miris","1144–1180":"1144–1180","1163–1233":"1163–1233.gads","1185–1206":"1185–1206.gads","1185–1203":"1185–1203","1206–1283":"1206.gads–1283","1143–1175":"1143–1175.gads","1122–Female":"1122–mirusi","1143":"1143","1175":"1175. gads","1142":"1142","Abt 1159":"ap 1159. gadu","1185":"1185","1163":"1163","1283":"1283","1180":"1180","1206":"1206. gads","1203":"1203","1233":"1233. gads","1122":"1122","1144":"1144","about 1163":"ap 1163. gadu","Corstorphine, Midlothian, Scotland":"Corstorphine, Midlothian, Scotland","Scotland, United Kingdom":"Skotija, Lielbritānija","Dalkeith Palace, Midlothian, Scotland":"Dalkeith, Midlothian, Scotland","Dalkeith, Midlothian, Scotland":"Dalkeith, Midlothian, Skotija, Lielbritānija"},"mg":{"about 1163–1233":"tany ho any amin'ny 1163–1233","1142–Male":"1142–Maty","1144–1180":"1144–1180","1163–1233":"1163–1233","1185–1206":"1185–1206","1185–1203":"1185–1203","1206–1283":"1206–1283","1143–1175":"1143–1175","1122–Female":"1122–Maty","1143":"1143","1175":"1175","1142":"1142","Abt 1159":"tany ho any amin'ny 1159","1185":"1185","1163":"1163","1283":"1283","1180":"1180","1206":"1206","1203":"1203","1233":"1233","1122":"1122","1144":"1144","about 1163":"tany ho any amin'ny 1163","Corstorphine, Midlothian, Scotland":"Corstorphine, Midlothian, Scotland","Scotland, United Kingdom":"Écosse, United Kingdom","Dalkeith Palace, Midlothian, Scotland":"Dalkeith, Midlothian, Scotland","Dalkeith, Midlothian, Scotland":"Dalkeith, Midlothian, Écosse, United Kingdom"},"ms":{"about 1163–1233":"kira–kira 1163–1233","1142–Male":"1142–Mati","1144–1180":"1144–1180","1163–1233":"1163–1233","1185–1206":"1185–1206","1185–1203":"1185–1203","1206–1283":"12